<codeline lineno="6"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="7"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@section<sp/>ModelTemplate_intro<sp/>Introduction</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="8"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>The<sp/>`ModelTemplate`<sp/>class,<sp/>implemented<sp/>in<sp/>Cython,<sp/>serves<sp/>as<sp/>a<sp/>foundational<sp/>base<sp/>for<sp/>machine<sp/>learning<sp/>models<sp/>within<sp/>the<sp/>AnalysisG<sp/>framework.<sp/>It<sp/>provides<sp/>a<sp/>standardized<sp/>interface<sp/>for<sp/>managing<sp/>input<sp/>and<sp/>output<sp/>features<sp/>for<sp/>graph-based<sp/>data,<sp/>as<sp/>well<sp/>as<sp/>configuring<sp/>the<sp/>computational<sp/>device<sp/>and<sp/>model<sp/>checkpoints.<sp/>This<sp/>class<sp/>is<sp/>designed<sp/>to<sp/>be<sp/>inherited<sp/>by<sp/>specific<sp/>model<sp/>implementations,<sp/>offering<sp/>common<sp/>functionalities<sp/>and<sp/>efficient<sp/>interaction<sp/>with<sp/>an<sp/>underlying<sp/>C++<sp/>model<sp/>structure.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="9"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="10"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@section<sp/>ModelTemplate_class<sp/>The<sp/>ModelTemplate<sp/>Class</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="11"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>`ModelTemplate`<sp/>is<sp/>a<sp/>`cdef<sp/>class`,<sp/>indicating<sp/>its<sp/>implementation<sp/>as<sp/>a<sp/>Cython<sp/>extension<sp/>type.<sp/>This<sp/>design<sp/>allows<sp/>for<sp/>direct<sp/>and<sp/>optimized<sp/>interaction<sp/>with<sp/>C++<sp/>objects<sp/>and<sp/>types,<sp/>which<sp/>is<sp/>crucial<sp/>for<sp/>performance<sp/>in<sp/>machine<sp/>learning<sp/>applications.<sp/>It<sp/>encapsulates<sp/>a<sp/>pointer<sp/>(`self.nn_ptr`)<sp/>to<sp/>a<sp/>C++<sp/>`model_template`<sp/>object,<sp/>managing<sp/>its<sp/>lifecycle<sp/>and<sp/>exposing<sp/>its<sp/>parameters<sp/>as<sp/>Python<sp/>properties.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="12"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="13"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@subsection<sp/>ModelTemplate_cinit_dealloc<sp/>Constructors<sp/>and<sp/>Destructors</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="14"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`__cinit__(self)`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="15"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>The<sp/>Cython<sp/>&quot;constructor&quot;<sp/>equivalent,<sp/>called<sp/>during<sp/>object<sp/>allocation.<sp/>It<sp/>initializes<sp/>`self.rename`<sp/>to<sp/>`False`.<sp/>If<sp/>the<sp/>instance<sp/>is<sp/>not<sp/>`ModelTemplate`<sp/>itself<sp/>(i.e.,<sp/>it&apos;s<sp/>a<sp/>subclass),<sp/>it<sp/>returns<sp/>immediately.<sp/>Otherwise,<sp/>it<sp/>initializes<sp/>a<sp/>new<sp/>C++<sp/>`model_template`<sp/>object<sp/>and<sp/>assigns<sp/>its<sp/>pointer<sp/>to<sp/>`self.nn_ptr`.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="16"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="17"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`__init__(self)`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="18"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>The<sp/>standard<sp/>Python<sp/>initializer,<sp/>intentionally<sp/>left<sp/>empty<sp/>as<sp/>primary<sp/>initialization<sp/>is<sp/>handled<sp/>by<sp/>`__cinit__`.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="19"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="20"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`__dealloc__(self)`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="21"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>The<sp/>Cython<sp/>&quot;destructor&quot;<sp/>equivalent,<sp/>called<sp/>upon<sp/>object<sp/>deallocation.<sp/>If<sp/>the<sp/>instance<sp/>is<sp/>not<sp/>`ModelTemplate`<sp/>itself,<sp/>it<sp/>returns.<sp/>Otherwise,<sp/>it<sp/>deallocates<sp/>the<sp/>C++<sp/>`model_template`<sp/>object<sp/>pointed<sp/>to<sp/>by<sp/>`self.nn_ptr`,<sp/>ensuring<sp/>proper<sp/>memory<sp/>management.</highlight></codeline>
