<codeline lineno="25"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>An<sp/>internal<sp/>helper<sp/>method<sp/>to<sp/>convert<sp/>a<sp/>C++<sp/>`map&lt;string,<sp/>string&gt;`<sp/>(passed<sp/>as<sp/>a<sp/>pointer)<sp/>into<sp/>a<sp/>Python<sp/>dictionary.<sp/>It<sp/>iterates<sp/>through<sp/>the<sp/>C++<sp/>map<sp/>and<sp/>uses<sp/>`env`<sp/>to<sp/>convert<sp/>C++<sp/>strings<sp/>to<sp/>Python<sp/>strings<sp/>for<sp/>both<sp/>keys<sp/>and<sp/>values.</highlight></codeline>
