<codeline lineno="30"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>An<sp/>internal<sp/>helper<sp/>method<sp/>to<sp/>convert<sp/>a<sp/>Python<sp/>dictionary<sp/>into<sp/>a<sp/>C++<sp/>`map&lt;string,<sp/>string&gt;`.<sp/>It<sp/>iterates<sp/>through<sp/>the<sp/>Python<sp/>dictionary<sp/>and<sp/>uses<sp/>`enc`<sp/>to<sp/>convert<sp/>Python<sp/>strings<sp/>to<sp/>C++<sp/>strings<sp/>for<sp/>both<sp/>keys<sp/>and<sp/>values.<sp/>If<sp/>`self.rename`<sp/>is<sp/>`False`,<sp/>it<sp/>also<sp/>sets<sp/>the<sp/>C++<sp/>model&apos;s<sp/>name<sp/>to<sp/>the<sp/>Python<sp/>class<sp/>name.</highlight></codeline>
